Comment: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OPENING/ENDING/SIGNS


Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a few minutes, the opening ceremony for Daihaseisai will begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, at Academy City, the streets are bustling about with the parents and siblings of our students!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maid bentos here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like Academy City's famous maid bentos?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryouran Kasei Girl's School maid's—\Nor rather, maid-in-training bentos?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, there are a lot of schools in Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a city where all the world's top educational institutions are concentrated into one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, that was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you happen to know where Tokiwadai Middle School is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokiwadai... Tokiwadai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not here. Maybe it isn't open to the public?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:00:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then where on Earth is Mikoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Mikoto-san a sister of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, Touya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you at it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really isn't here! What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:11.96,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mother... what do you mean "again?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Isn't that Touma-san over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.83,0:01:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose, I'll do a penalty game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything goes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.34,0:01:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for you if you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.67,0:01:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do anything you—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.68,0:01:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really all the confidence you have after running your mouth like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.32,0:01:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, you're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you cry your way out of it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.86,0:01:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikoto-chan looks happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:57.42,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(670,849)\pos(836,560)}#08 Daihaseisai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Daihaseisai will begin soon, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you be paying them a visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think I can let people see me like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's not hesitate to continue our conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the magicians who've infiltrated Academy City?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.78,0:02:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're taking the chance while city security is relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've managed to confirm that there are two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A high ranking member of the Roman Catholic Church, and a courier she hired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their objective is a particular object.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A particular object?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stab Sword."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it can slay a dragon and pin it to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If successfully handed over, the Church of England will be in a rather dreadful predicament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A so-called "tactical weapon" for your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the biggest issue:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:03:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The trade for the sword is happening within Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to get that boy to be the travel guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just ate breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's such a delicious smell everywhere that I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan's food culture is the essence of food temptation!{日本の料理文化は食という名の誘惑の塊かも}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can walk around later and check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.26,0:03:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first match is starting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the events I'm participating in today are marked in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Touma seems really dull today...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we really have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does everyone look so weary before we've even started?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:04:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used up what little energy we had fighting over what strategy to use to defeat the other schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your priorities straight!{本末転倒じゃねか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what student matches are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this lack of spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kamijou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you infected everyone else with your laziness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only just got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So everyone basically lost their motivation because you showed up late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were later than I was, Fukiyose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had committee duties to take care of, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijou-san has gotten himself into an unfortunate situation and he can't get up for the time being!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just anemia getting to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this sports drink will fix that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate people who blame bad luck or fate for their own lack of resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's lost their motivation because of your laziness, so you'd better get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None whatsoever, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody even wants to play Pole Assault anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This may seriously be hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I realize that our equipment and curriculum are lacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that isn't the fault of the students!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it because their results are so low that the administrative board refuses to raise funding?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have it pretty rough, teaching a bunch of failures like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Students can't simply be labeled as successes or failures!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just have their own personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty idealistic opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pole Assault that's starting now...{}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be sure to completely crush those hopeless failures at your school.{お宅の落ちこぼれたちを完膚なきまでに撃破して差し上げますよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our students aren't hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to do this or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First match: Pole Assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The various school teams are entering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a reckless guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way they can beat our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could she be suffering from heatstroke?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you really are hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Miss Short-Hair doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheering for Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why would I cheer for that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came to see which school will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's obvious my school will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd do anything I asked...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he look so determined?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he seriously going to try to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he going to make me do once he wins?!{What does he have planned for me to do?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get set...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you all go so far just to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you won, seeing you all bruised like that makes me...{makes Sensei...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, she's so hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left it in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I came here to get my cellphone so I could contact someone I was separated from.{is there better wording for this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have any bad intentions...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you just crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you answer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your battery's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevermind that, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me something to eat, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to the stands, there are mountains of food there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mountains!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.94,0:09:27.60,TOARUSigns3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\blur1\bord5\3c&H9874D1&\c&HF1EFE8&\pos(639,169)}NO ENTRY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry, there's a parade coming through here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only need to get over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a subway you can use to cross the street if you go about 3km west.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3km...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'll just have to wait until the Ball Rolling event is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I've got you! You're my ticket to victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:10:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner of the Borrowed Item Race is Misaka Mikoto of Tokiwadai Middle School!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Borrowed Item Race?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. I had to find a high school student who participated in the first event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you just happen to fit the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there a bunch of other people who'd fit—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that for?{are you doing?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, drink this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other choice, so I'll let you have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see, when I imagined you resting in bed while the rest of us were working in this blazing heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't stop myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to help us out, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you very much, my dear friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are there any problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After taking first place, Misaka Mikoto remains in tip-top shape{same meaning?}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She continues to make everything look so easy.{??????????????????????}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my beloved Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here we see her taking care of her partner who ran with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill him!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.24,0:11:37.37,TOARUSigns3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\blur1\bord3\3c&H9874D1&\c&HF1EFE8&\pos(514,232)\frx14\fry50\frz342.008}NO ENTRY
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find Index.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will she be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:12:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Academy City is most likely relaxing{restraining} its security in order to attract a bigger audience.{not cause distress to the public}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And magicians are taking this chance to infiltrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've only confirmed two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidvia Lorenzetti of the Roman Catholic Church, and the courier she hired, Oriana Thompson.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Courier?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're making a trade with the Church's spiritual weapon here in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Academy City as far from the occult as you can get?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's precisely why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a place where neither the science side nor magic side can interfere easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the only people who can act are your buddies already in Academy City.{assuming he means relatives by shiriai, need to watch the rest for more context & definitive answer}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Kanzaki then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she a Saint or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use Kanzaki, especially not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not with the spiritual weapon being what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan, the name of the weapon is "Stab Sword."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:13:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it can kill any Saint with a single strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Kamijou Touma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how the Son of God was killed on the cross, Kami-yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he... nailed there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was stabbed to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stab Sword is a weapon that extracts the religious meaning of the nailing and stabbing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and amplifies, concentrates, and focuses it to its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would have no effect on normal humans, but it has a one-hit-kill ability if used against a Saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do the magicians have planned, trading something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Preparing for war, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saints have power equivalent to that of a nuclear weapon in the magical world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are plenty of magicians who aren't Saints, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd imagine they could fight without Kanzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about whether they'd actually win or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wars can start simply because one side has the illusion of having a winning chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:12.86,TOARUSigns3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz90\fs55\pos(101,167)\c&HC6C3BE&\3c&H3D2CA4&\bord5\blur2\1a&HFF}NO ENTRY
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.81,0:14:12.86,TOARUSigns3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz90\fs55\pos(101,167)\c&HC6C3BE&\3c&H3D2CA4&\blur4\bord0}NO ENTRY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait, if this is that serious a problem, shouldn't we ask Index for her help?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use that forbidden index{says the regular noun, not the proper noun} for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let her near any of this, or even let her know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if anything were to happen, she'd become the center of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's{\i0} how many magicians are looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she were to be discovered, magicians would come flooding in, aiming for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, we have to do something about it without letting Index notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I rushed back to you after hearing from Yomikawa-sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really panicked since you looked almost like a leftover shriveled vegetable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Touma go, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... you just had lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Touma and I be seperated like this for the rest of the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to enjoy Daihaseisai with Kamijou-chan don't you, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something you can participate in, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... did you really get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you walking around looking like a hero who's about to face the final boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got an expression on like you're about to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:15:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not go eat something if you're hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that, have you seen Index anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the Sister walking over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like she was being dragged somewhere by that famous little teacher at your school!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Index?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's just you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Index?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It pains me to make you change here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times does this make it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well... Index-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to get so serious about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to look for Tsukiyomi-sensei for some committee work...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you put even a little effort into making this festival a success?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What event is our school in now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. If your brain isn't getting enough nutrients, go get some sugar into your system!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kamijou-san's stupidity won't be cured with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel bad at all, hearing yourself say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the second-year girls' tug o' war and the third-year boys' restricted triathlon are on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which event will you go to support?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girls, I bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:17:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course, you {\i1}are{\i0} Kamijou after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least don't pull me by my neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kamijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you find Daihaseisai boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem restless...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like something else is on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're finding today boring, Kamijou, it means I'm not doing enough as a committee member...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I think it's boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess, as someone who worked so hard to come up with all this stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of want everyone to share fond memories of the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm just being selfish, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do have something bothering you, don't you? {This woman is going to have back problems before she hits 20}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me, Kamijou Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not used to such crowded areas...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your forehead is swelling up.{lit: getting red}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As an apology for bumping into you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! A kiss would be—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Oriana Thompson here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say your real name out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your voice audible to anyone around you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevermind that; I've run into some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the spell Onee-san cast on me was dispelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's turning me on for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such obscene things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countermeasures?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.47,0:20:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll have to lose that boy behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:27.97,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oriana runs around, toying with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl risks his life to investigate the spell she cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the place we found...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "Route Disturb."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths, this epic will begin!
